14
00:00:43,574 --> 00:00:45,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Same mission creates similar lives.</b></font>

15
00:00:45,794 --> 00:00:48,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But your passion for your dream will make a difference.</b></font>

16
00:00:48,494 --> 00:00:50,914
