(Let's go)</b></font>

28
00:01:27,064 --> 00:01:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, raise up your hands now.</b></font>

29
00:01:47,294 --> 00:01:50,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hakone's fog is nice.</b></font>

30
00:01:51,494 --> 00:01:54,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It hides the dirty side of reality.</b></font>

31
00:01:56,214 --> 00:02:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I stand still like this, there's
nothing other than absolute silence</b></font>

32
00:02:02,814 --> 00:02:04,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and overwhelming loneliness.</b></font>

33
00:02:08,114 --> 00:02:12,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the state of nirvana, right, Kaori?</b></font>

34
00:02:14,094 --> 00:02:19,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ever since I lost you, I feel like
 I've been standing in the fog.</b></font>

35
00:02:21,014 --> 00:02:26,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to have a race against
Ryosuke where we both bet our lives.</b></font>

36
00:02:26,144 --> 00:02:30,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll send one of us to your side.</b></font>

37
00:02:32,454 --> 00:02:34,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So make a choice.</b></font>

38
00:02:36,084 --> 00:02:39,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This time, follow your heart, Kaori.</b></font>

39
00:03:11,164 --> 00:03:13,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Long time no see, Ryosuke.</b></font>

40
00:03:17,914 --> 00:03:20,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You look a little neater, huh?</b></font>

41
00:03:22,604 --> 00:03:27,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's been a while, Hojo Rin.</b></font>

42
00:03:27,214 --> 00:03:27,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Senpai.</b></font>

43
00:03:42,014 --> 00:03:43,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've heard the story.</b></font>

44
00:03:43,914 --> 00:03:48,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I called Ryosuke's cell,
but it seems to be turned off.</b></font>

45
00:03:48,244 --> 00:03:51,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I left a message,
but I haven't heard back.</b></font>

46
00:03:51,214 --> 00:03:54,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been told that he's not
in the college lab either.</b></font>

47
00:03:54,184 --> 00:03:59,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Ryosuke secretly modified his FC,
I'm sure he must have a reason for it.</b></font>

48
00:04:00,964 --> 00:04:06,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Matsumoto is the one who's been 
tuning and maintaining the FC</b></font>

49
00:04:06,414 --> 00:04:10,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I've tried calling him to find 
out if he knows something, but</b></font>

50
00:04:10,474 --> 00:04:12,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't reach him either.</b></font>

51
00:04:12,804 --> 00:04:16,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something is definitely not
right with both of them missing.</b></font>

52
00:04:17,844 --> 00:04:22,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If that's the case, I'll just ignore this.</b></font>

53
00:04:22,284 --> 00:04:23,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

54
00:04:23,664 --> 00:04:27,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean, for the time being it's
pointless for us to get upset over this.</b></font>

55
00:04:27,884 --> 00:04:31,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How could you not be? 
Aren't you worried?</b></font>

56
00:04:31,874 --> 00:04:35,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My brother must have a 
significant reason for doing this,</b></font>

57
00:04:35,294 --> 00:04:38,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>including going solo behind our back.</b></font>

58
00:04:39,594 --> 00:04:43,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's always been been like this.
You know that, don't you?</b></font>

59
00:04:43,014 --> 00:04:45,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He always makes the right choice.</b></font>

60
00:04:45,914 --> 00:04:50,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll come back and feign 
ignorance as if nothing happened.</b></font>

61
00:04:50,504 --> 00:04:54,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just have faith in him and wait.
There's no point in worrying.</b></font>

62
00:04:55,654 --> 00:04:57,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's just act like we normally do.</b></font>

63
00:04:57,664 --> 00:05:01,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What we should be doing now
is preparing for the final battle.</b></font>

64
00:05:02,994 --> 00:05:05,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what my brother
would say if he were here.</b></font>

65
00:05:07,034 --> 00:05:10,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no need to worry
about a remote possibility.</b></font>

66
00:05:10,094 --> 00:05:13,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's Japan's most ingenious street racer.</b></font>

67
00:05:13,514 --> 00:05:15,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget that.</b></font>

68
00:05:17,164 --> 00:05:21,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Act 9  [ Grim Reaper ]</b></font>

69
00:05:28,414 --> 00:05:30,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke</b></font>

70
00:05:31,414 --> 00:05:35,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be waiting here, so please
pick me up when you're done.</b></font>

71
00:05:36,324 --> 00:05:40,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I plan to return to Gunma
in your car's passenger seat.</b></font>

72
00:05:40,664 --> 00:05:43,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I haven't thought about any other way.</b></font>

73
00:05:43,864 --> 00:05:46,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if it takes several days, I'll be waiting...</b></font>

74
00:05:47,664 --> 00:05:51,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if it rains, to the point where I get soaked...</b></font>

75
00:05:53,014 --> 00:05:57,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In other words, if you
don't return, I'll die here.</b></font>

76
00:06:01,464 --> 00:06:03,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can really see you doing that.</b></font>

77
00:06:04,884 --> 00:06:06,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll return no matter what.</b></font>

78
00:06:06,914 --> 00:06:07,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

79
00:06:25,114 --> 00:06:27,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a promise, Ryosuke.</b></font>

80
00:06:30,714 --> 00:06:32,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please come back safely.</b></font>

81
00:06:39,924 --> 00:06:41,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A white FC?</b></font>

82
00:06:41,644 --> 00:06:42,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

83
00:06:42,914 --> 00:06:46,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A guy saw it when he was
visiting Akagi the other day.</b></font>

84
00:06:46,734 --> 00:06:50,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you mean Takahashi
Ryosuke is making a comeback?</b></font>

85
00:06:50,604 --> 00:06:52,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way.</b></font>

86
00:06:52,414 --> 00:06:55,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's probably a copy by a hardcore fan.</b></font>

87
00:06:55,084 --> 00:06:56,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That could be the case.</b></font>

88
00:06:57,774 --> 00:07:01,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Remember those impersonators the other day?</b></font>

89
00:07:01,674 --> 00:07:03,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not likely.</b></font>

90
00:07:03,664 --> 00:07:05,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akagi is Takahashi Ryosuke's home ground.</b></font>

91
00:07:05,914 --> 00:07:07,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Any impersonator would
get caught immediately.</b></font>

92
00:07:07,914 --> 00:07:09,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's right.</b></font>

93
00:07:10,314 --> 00:07:13,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, did Takumi say anything?</b></font>

94
00:07:13,564 --> 00:07:15,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not a thing.</b></font>

95
00:07:16,314 --> 00:07:17,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd better call him.</b></font>

96
00:07:18,564 --> 00:07:23,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he ignores his best friend like he did the other day, I'll chew him out.</b></font>

97
00:07:28,264 --> 00:07:31,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke did?</b></font>

98
00:07:31,074 --> 00:07:34,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I don't know anything about it.</b></font>

99
00:07:34,504 --> 00:07:38,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe it's just a look alike.</b></font>

100
00:07:38,254 --> 00:07:39,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, bye.</b></font>

101
00:07:41,284 --> 00:07:44,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong?
Another impersonator?</b></font>

102
00:07:44,424 --> 00:07:48,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, no, I don't think it's that serious.</b></font>

103
00:07:50,464 --> 00:07:54,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But come to think of it, we have
to thank those impersonators.</b></font>

104
00:07:55,794 --> 00:08:00,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, I met you because of them.</b></font>

105
00:08:01,634 --> 00:08:02,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess so.</b></font>

106
00:08:03,834 --> 00:08:07,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi, why don't we go
somewhere together again?</b></font>

107
00:08:07,314 --> 00:08:09,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've been to the beach,
so how about the mountains?</b></font>

108
00:08:33,774 --> 00:08:34,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is way too risky.</b></font>

109
00:08:36,064 --> 00:08:41,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never seen such a high speed 
downhill stage like this anywhere.</b></font>

110
00:08:41,134 --> 00:08:45,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's really disadvantageous to be in
the lead position against a local.</b></font>

111
00:08:46,644 --> 00:08:51,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He hasn't had time to become familiar
with the renewed FC after his hiatus.</b></font>

112
00:08:53,274 --> 00:09:01,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But all I can do now is believe in the super driving
sense from his days as Akagi's White Comet.</b></font>

113
00:09:02,784 --> 00:09:03,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke</b></font>

114
00:09:16,004 --> 00:09:17,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Three years ago</b></font>

115
00:09:17,714 --> 00:09:18,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Eh?</b></font>

116
00:09:19,214 --> 00:09:23,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I fell in love with someone.</b></font>

117
00:09:23,764 --> 00:09:30,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She was my senior by one year at college,
and a type of person I hadn't met before.</b></font>

118
00:09:32,314 --> 00:09:37,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Free spirited, half childish, half mature.</b></font>

119
00:09:41,014 --> 00:09:45,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sometimes strong willed, but sometimes weak, a person with lots of contradictions.</b></font>

120
00:09:53,074 --> 00:09:57,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that's probably why I was attracted to her.</b></font>

121
00:09:57,714 --> 00:10:01,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lost my head over her to the 
extent that I couldn't control myself.</b></font>

122
00:10:02,974 --> 00:10:06,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's out of character for me, I guess.</b></font>

123
00:10:08,334 --> 00:10:15,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I haven't told anyone about this, but can 
you bear with my little story, Matsumoto?</b></font>

124
00:10:41,784 --> 00:10:47,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cornering potential is equal, but my 
car has significantly greater power.</b></font>

125
00:10:49,334 --> 00:10:53,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As for braking, his car has the
advantage because of the lighter weight.</b></font>

126
00:10:53,664 --> 00:10:57,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It will become more apparent
toward the end of the battle.</b></font>

127
00:10:59,664 --> 00:11:03,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that works fine for me.</b></font>

128
00:11:05,884 --> 00:11:11,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I can't stop, I won't be able to
avoid slamming my car into his.</b></font>

129
00:11:18,344 --> 00:11:23,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There will only be one round.
If you manage to get away, you win.</b></font>

130
00:11:26,914 --> 00:11:28,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I won't let you.</b></font>

131
00:11:36,534 --> 00:11:37,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke</b></font>

132
00:11:56,664 --> 00:11:59,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why do you think you were born?</b></font>

133
00:12:02,364 --> 00:12:04,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Have you ever thought about it, Ryosuke?</b></font>

134
00:12:10,994 --> 00:12:14,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There you go again. 
Another philosophical question.</b></font>

135
00:12:14,214 --> 00:12:17,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't dodge my question, try to answer it.</b></font>

136
00:12:17,114 --> 00:12:19,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you really want to do?</b></font>

137
00:12:27,464 --> 00:12:31,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you really want to succeed your parents?</b></font>

138
00:12:31,464 --> 00:12:35,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you attending college because
you actually want to become a doctor?</b></font>

139
00:12:40,264 --> 00:12:43,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't be happy with that.</b></font>

140
00:12:43,464 --> 00:12:48,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's rather sad if you can't 
choose what to do with your life.</b></font>

141
00:12:49,714 --> 00:12:52,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're hitting a sore spot, Kaori.</b></font>

142
00:12:53,144 --> 00:12:56,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What makes you happy?</b></font>

143
00:12:56,354 --> 00:12:58,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What makes you truly happy?</b></font>

144
00:13:00,004 --> 00:13:01,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you have a dream?</b></font>

145
00:13:02,854 --> 00:13:05,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is your dream, Ryosuke?</b></font>

146
00:13:32,164 --> 00:13:34,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Any news?</b></font>

147
00:13:34,014 --> 00:13:37,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I spotted the Grim Reaper's R32.</b></font>

148
00:13:37,814 --> 00:13:41,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'll pass by your location,
chasing a white car at high speed.</b></font>

149
00:13:42,614 --> 00:13:45,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please be very careful, Ikeda.</b></font>

150
00:13:45,514 --> 00:13:46,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Got it.</b></font>

151
00:14:16,064 --> 00:14:20,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've finally got you, Grim Reaper.</b></font>

152
00:14:40,754 --> 00:14:46,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Team Spiral is proud to be the
neighborhood watch of Hakone.</b></font>

153
00:14:46,034 --> 00:14:49,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We won't forgive anyone who breaks
the rules of the mountain pass.</b></font>

154
00:14:50,164 --> 00:14:52,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your insolence ends today.</b></font>

155
00:14:54,564 --> 00:14:59,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, who's driving that white FC?</b></font>

156
00:15:01,454 --> 00:15:06,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How reckless of you to take the lead
position against the Grim Reaper.</b></font>

157
00:15:06,614 --> 00:15:08,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must have nerves of steel.</b></font>

158
00:15:10,164 --> 00:15:11,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could that be</b></font>

159
00:15:11,714 --> 00:15:13,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>him?!</b></font>

160
00:15:19,164 --> 00:15:23,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke, there's something I haven't told you yet.</b></font>

161
00:15:42,014 --> 00:15:46,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a fiancé chosen by my parents.</b></font>

162
00:15:48,064 --> 00:15:51,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll have to marry him in a few years.</b></font>

163
00:15:59,974 --> 00:16:02,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a bad joke, Kaori.</b></font>

164
00:16:05,324 --> 00:16:10,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you really want to 
follow your parents wishes?</b></font>

165
00:16:10,214 --> 00:16:13,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not like you at all.</b></font>

166
00:16:14,034 --> 00:16:17,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You just don't know the true me.</b></font>

167
00:16:20,764 --> 00:16:23,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then I'll begin to discover it from now on.</b></font>

168
00:16:24,114 --> 00:16:27,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not going to give you up.</b></font>

169
00:16:28,814 --> 00:16:30,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No</b></font>

170
00:16:35,014 --> 00:16:37,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please give up.</b></font>

171
00:16:44,214 --> 00:16:47,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you crying?</b></font>

172
00:16:49,934 --> 00:16:54,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll protect you no matter what.</b></font>

173
00:17:09,154 --> 00:17:11,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong, Ryosuke?</b></font>

174
00:17:11,134 --> 00:17:15,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see a slight hesitation in your corner entries.</b></font>

175
00:17:15,034 --> 00:17:17,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you scared of this
super high speed stage?</b></font>

176
00:17:17,564 --> 00:17:19,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Or is it because of your hiatus?</b></font>

177
00:17:23,494 --> 00:17:25,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're so naive, Ryosuke.</b></font>

178
00:17:25,464 --> 00:17:27,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you're spacing out, I'll wake you up.</b></font>

179
00:17:30,914 --> 00:17:32,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He did it already.</b></font>

180
00:17:33,604 --> 00:17:40,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rear wheel drive cars are defenseless against that kind
of push right after the turn in when the car is unstable.</b></font>

181
00:17:40,354 --> 00:17:43,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Grim Reaper did it on purpose.</b></font>

182
00:17:43,714 --> 00:17:45,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please recover.</b></font>

183
00:17:57,844 --> 00:17:59,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, that was incredible.</b></font>

184
00:18:00,414 --> 00:18:04,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's more like it.
That was my way of saying "Hi."</b></font>

185
00:18:14,714 --> 00:18:16,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can control the car.</b></font>

186
00:18:16,564 --> 00:18:20,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's well tuned, as always, Matsumoto.</b></font>

187
00:18:20,764 --> 00:18:26,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now I know I can push myself
to the limit without hesitation.</b></font>

188
00:18:27,514 --> 00:18:30,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here comes the next one. It'll be harder.</b></font>

189
00:18:35,704 --> 00:18:39,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Grim Reaper is acting
differently from before.</b></font>

190
00:18:39,214 --> 00:18:41,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's seriously trying to...</b></font>

191
00:18:51,364 --> 00:18:52,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He missed?!</b></font>

192
00:18:53,314 --> 00:18:56,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Grim Reaper's serious 
attempt to crash was dodged.</b></font>

193
00:18:57,744 --> 00:18:59,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What incredible acceleration.</b></font>

194
00:18:59,824 --> 00:19:03,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no more doubt about that FC.</b></font>

195
00:19:03,214 --> 00:19:06,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The charismatic driver, who was once
the best in northern Kanto, has returned.</b></font>

196
00:19:09,414 --> 00:19:11,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What made him do that?</b></font>

197
00:19:16,634 --> 00:19:17,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke...</b></font>

198
00:19:28,624 --> 00:19:30,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

199
00:19:31,314 --> 00:19:35,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Grim Reaper is acting strange,
showing true hostile intent.</b></font>

200
00:19:36,114 --> 00:19:41,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The other guy is well aware of it,
but he isn't even trying to escape.</b></font>

201
00:19:41,964 --> 00:19:44,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is no ordinary battle.</b></font>

202
00:19:44,964 --> 00:19:48,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looks like I ran into
an extraordinary situation.</b></font>

203
00:19:51,114 --> 00:19:56,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just like you, Ryosuke.
Your earlier hesitation is gone.</b></font>

204
00:19:56,954 --> 00:19:59,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've got incredible adaptability.</b></font>

205
00:19:59,514 --> 00:20:02,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a much better 
driver than I expected.</b></font>

206
00:20:08,734 --> 00:20:12,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you nearby, Kaori, watching us?</b></font>

207
00:20:14,714 --> 00:20:16,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I dedicate this battle to you.</b></font>

208
00:20:18,264 --> 00:20:22,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if I die here tonight, I won't regret it.</b></font>

209
00:20:22,814 --> 00:20:24,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not afraid of anything.</b></font>

210
00:20:51,864 --> 00:20:54,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry, Hojo.</b></font>

211
00:20:54,664 --> 00:20:56,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't marry you.</b></font>

212
00:21:01,114 --> 00:21:06,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on, that's so abrupt. Tell me why.</b></font>

213
00:21:06,524 --> 00:21:09,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This has nothing to do with
our parents arrangement.</b></font>

214
00:21:10,744 --> 00:21:16,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you know that I love you
from the bottom of my heart?</b></font>

215
00:21:50,214 --> 00:21:51,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is scary.</b></font>

216
00:21:51,994 --> 00:21:54,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Their tension is off the scale.</b></font>

217
00:21:54,364 --> 00:21:58,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm having a hard time keeping up with them, 
much less cutting in between them.</b></font>

218
00:21:59,784 --> 00:22:03,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Besides, that Takahashi Ryosuke,</b></font>

219
00:22:03,914 --> 00:22:08,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard he was the logical type, but that's not true.</b></font>

220
00:22:08,704 --> 00:22:11,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Only a genius could pull off this kind of driving.</b></font>

221
00:22:11,854 --> 00:22:16,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's almost a miracle for a 
non local to maintain this high pace.</b></font>

222
00:22:18,034 --> 00:22:25,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This course is so unique that even the
locals don't push themselves to the limit,</b></font>

223
00:22:25,654 --> 00:22:27,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because you only have one life.</b></font>

224
00:22:41,454 --> 00:22:42,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So fast.</b></font>

225
00:22:42,714 --> 00:22:46,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His handling of the rotary
engine is almost an art.</b></font>

226
00:22:46,104 --> 00:22:50,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, even being known as the logical type, it's because he
has both the sense of a genius and an all too clever mind?</b></font>

227
00:22:52,214 --> 00:22:55,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the true nature of Takahashi Ryosuke.</b></font>

228
00:23:02,404 --> 00:23:08,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the Grim Reaper will show his
truly frightening nature up ahead.</b></font>

229
00:23:41,414 --> 00:23:42,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke.</b></font>

230
00:23:45,614 --> 00:23:47,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a mysterious person.</b></font>

231
00:23:51,914 --> 00:23:57,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're younger than me, but more 
composed, which irritates me a bit.</b></font>

232
00:23:57,214 --> 00:24:01,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you're always honest, 
kind and strong minded</b></font>

233
00:24:02,564 --> 00:24:06,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the type of person who
can make a woman happy.</b></font>

234
00:24:10,034 --> 00:24:13,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not sure if I can be the one.</b></font>

235
00:24:15,114 --> 00:24:19,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe I don't deserve your feelings.</b></font>

236
00:24:25,974 --> 00:24:27,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wish I could</b></font>

237
00:24:40,814 --> 00:24:43,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>be by your side forever.</b></font>

238
00:25:39,014 --> 00:25:44,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even when night falls, the scenery remains unchanged.</b></font>

239
00:25:44,014 --> 00:25:48,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Looking back at the path I've taken.</b></font>

240
00:25:48,904 --> 00:25:53,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sadness, happiness, incurable pains.</b></font>

241
00:25:53,414 --> 00:26:03,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Realizing that there are too many to count, as I walk alone.</b></font>

242
00:25:59,214 --> 00:26:01,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Countless number of memorable scenes.</b></font>

243
00:26:01,754 --> 00:26:04,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We lived through the hustle and bustle.</b></font>

244
00:26:04,154 --> 00:26:06,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sometimes we argued, sometimes we understood.</b></font>

245
00:26:06,494 --> 00:26:09,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It wasn't always pretty, but I keep the truth to myself</b></font>

246
00:26:09,294 --> 00:26:12,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as I take a new step.</b></font>

247
00:26:12,224 --> 00:26:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rosy clouds embellish the city.</b></font>

248
00:26:16,974 --> 00:26:23,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I quietly ask about my future.</b></font>

249
00:26:23,004 --> 00:26:26,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The sky remains silent.</b></font>

250
00:26:26,774 --> 00:26:36,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Only illuminating this path before me.</b></font>

251
00:26:36,114 --> 00:26:38,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Feel the translucent scenery.</b></font>

252
00:26:40,944 --> 00:26:43,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The setting sun plays a melody.</b></font>

253
00:26:45,824 --> 00:26:48,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Feel the translucent scenery.</b></font>

254
00:26:50,674 --> 00:26:52,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The setting sun plays a melody.</b></font>

